Note on wordlist content: the underlying Changde-dialect glossary
(skills/changde-dialect/references/glossary.md) is derived from
《常德方言词语汇1000》, compiled by 水兵1986 and originally published on
Meipian (https://www.meipian.cn/m5r5mum), whose author explicitly invited
readers to revise and supplement the list ("欢迎修订补充完善"). It is
included here under that invitation, with attribution. If you are the
original author or a rights holder and have concerns about this reuse,
please open an issue and it will be addressed promptly.
